                     <interp inst="t17790519-23-off132" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17790519-23-off132" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing a piece of printed linen cloth, containing eighteen yards, value 30 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17790519-23-victim256" type="victimName">
                     Isaac
                      Scott
                  <interp inst="t17790519-23-victim256" type="surname" value="Scott"></interp>
